{
  "stem": "14737.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 373.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there is such a thing in Hungary, the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is the, what you call it, the-- the anti-espionage division.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, who is a spy here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm a spy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're a spy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No one is a spy here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they figured out the Jews who are coming from the Carpathian, or the Russian, or that these Jews, especially, are spies.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what do they do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They come at night there, and they look for identification, and they see if someone is not from Budapest and the Carpathian.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because if they are Carpathian Jew, youngster, that he's also a spy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So people are avoiding at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're coming home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they're taking away the people to the headquarters at night, 1, 2 o'clock, down to these espionage police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the morning they let them out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What are you going to do with them?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They're not spies.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But these were very Hungarian who-- they-- they understood their-- their job is looking for spies.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And where are you looking for spies?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Jewish headquarters, and the Rumbach eventually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I live on Rumbach Street number 10.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Especially houses and the towns are living there Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you can mingle in the city, but over there you sleep at night, they know they're Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So me they didn't take.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One day, so they didn't take my identification, I speak Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they were not-- they were-- they were looking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was going on constantly, one street, another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Now, to go, for me, to live someplace else, I didn't have the means, I didn't have the money.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And besides, you cannot go to live there, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
